igate to “Settings” → “Help &amp; Support” → “Submit a Request”</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Website Contact Form:<a href=\"https://yoursecret.org/support#!\">[Submit a Support Ticket →]</a><br>(Quick and easy — we’ll get back to you within 1–3 business days.)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section-text-and-blocks {\"sectionTitle\":\"⏳ Our Response Time\",\"arrowImage\":\"http://yoursecret.loc/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/icon-19.svg\",\"btnCall\":\"We aim to respond as fast as possible because we know your voice matters.\"} -->\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section-text-and-blocks-inner -->\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Normal inquiries: 1–3 business days</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Urgent issues (account lockout, security concern): within 24 hours</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section-text-and-blocks-inner -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section-text-and-blocks -->\n\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section {\"sectionTitle\":\"🛡️ Your Privacy Comes First\",\"arrowImage\":\"http://yoursecret.loc/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/icon-8.svg\"} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Everything you send to Support is handled confidentially.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We do not disclose personal data unless legally required to do so.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your trust is our highest priority.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section {\"sectionTitle\":\"🧐 Before You Contact Us\",\"arrowImage\":\"http://yoursecret.loc/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/icon-20.svg\"} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please review our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://yoursecret.org/faq\">[FAQ Page]</a>&nbsp;— many common questions are answered there!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Check our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://yoursecret.org/community-guidelines\">[Community Guidelines]</a>&nbsp;- if your inquiry is about content or behavior.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section {\"lastInPage\":true} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Thank you for being part of YourSecret.<br>Together, we build a safe and inspiring space for everyone.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section -->', 'Support service', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'support-service', '', '', '2025-12-03 13:45:21', '2025-12-03 13:45:21', '', 0, 'http://yoursecret.loc/?page_id=55', 0, 'page', '', 0),
