(98, 1, '2025-12-02 14:18:43', '2025-12-02 14:18:43', '<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-hero {\"pageTitle\":\"How It Works\",\"sectionText\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eYourSecret is a platform built for emotional honesty, anonymous connection, and real self-expression.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eWe know the online world can feel noisy, fake, and overwhelming. That’s why we created something different:\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003eA place to feel, speak, and connect — without filters, without fear.\\u003c/p\\u003e\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section {\"sectionTitle\":\"🌐 What is YourSecret?\"} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>YourSecret is a safe, anonymous social space where you can:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Share your thoughts and secrets in real time</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Join meaningful anonymous conversations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Reflect on your emotions in a private diary</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Explore trending questions, challenges, and experiences</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No followers. No likes. No pressure. Just you and your truth.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section {\"sectionTitle\":\"⚫️ Step 1: Create Your Mask (No Identity Required)\"} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you first enter the platform, you answer a short set of creative questions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We use your answers to give you a&nbsp;<strong>unique \"mask\"</strong>&nbsp;— a visual avatar representing your mood, emotional state, and communication style.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It’s not a profile. It’s not a username. It’s a feeling-based identity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section {\"sectionTitle\":\"🔐 Step 2: Enter the Vault (Post Anonymously)\"} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>Vault</strong>&nbsp;is where users anonymously share thoughts, confessions, questions, or inspiration.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No names. No faces. Just pure self-expression.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Others can respond, react emotionally, or save posts that resonate. If two people share a connection — the system may suggest a deeper, anonymous conversation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section {\"sectionTitle\":\"🫵 Step 3: Join Live Anonymous Chats\"} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Feeling something right now?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hop into themed&nbsp;<strong>Anonymous Chats</strong>&nbsp;with others experiencing the same emotions or events — in real time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No usernames. No judgment. Just empathy and shared presence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section {\"sectionTitle\":\"📓 Step 4: Use Your Private Diary (with AI Insights)\"} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Keep a secure, private diary inside the app. Only you can see it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our AI assistant offers gentle questions, reflections, and emotional patterns to help you understand yourself better.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section -->\n\n<!-- wp:yoursecret/inner-page-section {\"sectionTitle\":\"💬 Step 5: Create Challenges, Polls, and Quests\"} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Spark anonymous debates. Launch emotional quests. Ask the community big questions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp